---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 145
By: Palladius
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Renunciation-Detachment=Eluding the Ego
---
Do not therefore ascribe blame or praise to the eating (or not eating) of
food, or to the drinking (or not drinking) of wine, but ascribe praise, or
woe, unto those who make use properly or improperly of meat and drink.
